# Next.js Project Setup and Basics

This repository contains the initial setup for the **SoloForge: Mastering Project Autonomy** project.  
The purpose of this repository is to provide a foundation for learning and practicing **Next.js**, **TypeScript**, and **Tailwind CSS**.  

### Objectives
- Set up a Next.js project using TypeScript and Tailwind CSS.
- Learn the basics of project structure, routing, and reusable components.
- Practice best practices in code organization, documentation, and styling.
